content.rendered:
Trailmax Electric Roller Shutter to suit Hilux 2018 – 2020

  • Electric retractable including two wireless remote controls
  • Remote operated internal LED light with multi output settings
  • 100% water proof
  • Durable black powder coat finish
  • Heavy Duty 200kg loading on top. Toughest in the market
  • Incorporated side mounting rails to accept optional cross bars
  • Compatible with sport bars, roll bars and rear racks
  • Safety anti jam function in built to protect from jamming body parts
  • Roller can stop at any opening via remote

 

Amazing 2 year warranty
